Description: The cmdlet 'New-AzNetAppFilesVolume' no longer supports the type 'System.Nullable`1[System.Int64]' for parameter 'UsageThreshold'.
Remediation: Change the type for parameter 'UsageThreshold' back to 'System.Nullable`1[System.Int64]'.

Description: The cmdlet 'New-AzNetAppFilesPool' no longer supports the type 'System.Nullable`1[System.Int64]' for parameter 'PoolSize'.
Remediation: Change the type for parameter 'PoolSize' back to 'System.Nullable`1[System.Int64]'.
